<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="a-great-good-deal">a great / good deal</h1>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>大量；很多：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Although she had never met that expert, she knew a great deal about him.
尽管她从来没有见过那位专家，但是她对他很了解。</p></div>

<h4 id="2">2.★ <strong>[常接比较级] ...得多：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>He ran a good deal faster than I.
他比我跑得快多了。</p></div></div>